      "backgroundColor": "#FDFEFB",
      "callsToAction": [],
      "text": "THE PROBLEM Most AI asks you to trust it. Agents say \"done\" without proof. They drift. They can't be audited. You can't ship — or sell, or pass an audit — on what you can't verify. SourceA is the controlled runtime that refuses to ship until it passes — and hands you the receipt.",
